Package: lcv
Title: League of Conservation Voters Congressional Scorecard Dataset
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Caspar", "Peter", , "cdpeter84@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive dataset of League of Conservation Voters (LCV) 
    Congressional Scorecard data spanning from 1971 to 2024. Includes tools 
    for downloading and processing environmental voting records for U.S. 
    House and Senate members.
